                             ↓
+----------------------------------------------------+
|           ORDER MANAGEMENT SYSTEM (OMS)            |
| Order orchestration | Order lifecycle management   |
+----------------------------+----------------------+
                             ↓
+----------------------------------------------------+
|               ORDER ROUTING ENGINE                 |
| Select optimal fulfilment node                    |
+----------------------------+----------------------+
                             ↓
+----------------------------------------------------+
